column1: # The readings for January-April 1936 are estimates and have been omitted.
# The reading for January 1940 is estimated for snow and has been retained.
# The readings for January and February 1950 are apportioned.
# The readings for February-April, August, November and December 1951 are estimates and have been omitted.
# The gauge and observer were previously at Cotescue Park.
